05:57.733 --> 05:59.569
Everybody out now!

06:00.653 --> 06:04.699
Everybody get out the building now!
Come on!

06:12.290 --> 06:13.457
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font>

06:13.541 --> 06:14.750
Gas attack.

06:14.876 --> 06:17.211
<i>Gas attack, gas attack.</i>

06:40.067 --> 06:43.404
<font color="#808080">MAN:</font> <font color="#D900D9">(OVER PA)</font> <i>Attention please.
Attention please.</i>

06:44.030 --> 06:46.449
<i>Please evacuate the building.</i>

06:46.782 --> 06:49.118
<i>Please do not
use the elevators.</i>

06:50.036 --> 06:53.372
<i>Make your way to the
nearest emergency exit.</i>

06:55.291 --> 06:58.502
<i>So when it happens,
as one day it must...</i>

06:58.628 --> 07:00.880
...it is imperative
not to panic.

07:01.005 --> 07:03.966
<i>Follow the drill and let
the training kick in.</i>

07:04.383 --> 07:06.469
<i>If circumstances allow...</i>

07:06.594 --> 07:09.096
...if, remember only if...

07:09.180 --> 07:12.391
<font color="#D900D9">(SIREN WAILING)</font>
<i>...in the event of an event...</i>

07:12.850 --> 07:14.560
<i>...or situation...</i>

07:14.685 --> 07:16.395
<i>...we are to remove,
where possible,</i>

07:16.479 --> 07:18.230
<i>the most valuable
item or items...</i>

07:18.356 --> 07:20.483
<i>...and take them to
a place of safety.</i>

07:20.608 --> 07:22.276
Stop right there.

07:25.029 --> 07:26.447
Step back.

07:28.282 --> 07:30.785
Remember, do not be a hero.

07:31.118 --> 07:32.536
Put it down.

07:35.581 --> 07:38.501
No piece of art is
worth a human life.

07:45.967 --> 07:47.677
<font color="#D900D9">(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)</font>
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMS)</font>

07:50.471 --> 07:51.555
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHS)</font>

07:54.100 --> 07:55.893
No, no, no...

07:58.062 --> 07:59.063
Don't.

08:00.439 --> 08:01.440
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font>

08:01.774 --> 08:02.775
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMS)</font>

08:08.572 --> 08:10.116
Fucking idiot!

08:13.369 --> 08:14.620
<font color="#D900D9">(WAILING CONTINUES)</font>

08:20.418 --> 08:21.585
<font color="#D900D9">(SIREN WAILING)</font>

08:24.213 --> 08:25.339
<font color="#D900D9">(COUGHS)</font>

08:41.230 --> 08:42.481
<font color="#D900D9">(COUGHING)</font>

09:01.208 --> 09:02.209
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font>

09:23.647 --> 09:24.732
<font color="#D900D9">(MAN CHUCKLING)</font>

09:33.491 --> 09:35.076
Riz, let's go.

10:00.851 --> 10:02.353
<font color="#D900D9">(UNZIPPING)</font>

10:10.027 --> 10:11.445
<font color="#D900D9">(SIREN WAILING)</font>

10:52.653 --> 10:54.238
<font color="#D900D9">(DRILL WHIRRING)</font>

11:05.457 --> 11:06.876
<font color="#D900D9">(INAUDIBLE)</font>

11:11.922 --> 11:13.299
<font color="#D900D9">(CAMERA CLICKING)</font>

11:18.304 --> 11:20.097
Afternoon, Sister.

11:21.557 --> 11:23.309
And how are you feeling?

11:23.392 --> 11:25.728
Um... Fine.

11:26.770 --> 11:28.147
Been up?
Mmm-hmm.

11:28.772 --> 11:31.942
Walking?
Yeah. Walking and everything.

11:32.067 --> 11:33.777
You know who you are?

11:34.945 --> 11:37.281
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font> Yeah, I think so.

11:37.406 --> 11:39.241
How do you feel
about going home?

11:41.285 --> 11:44.246
Jolly good! Right,
come on, troops, let's go.

11:58.802 --> 11:59.803
Thanks.

12:16.111 --> 12:18.113
Oh, fuck off!

12:18.989 --> 12:20.783
Fuck's sake.

12:32.211 --> 12:33.212
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING)</font>

12:55.526 --> 12:56.527
<font color="#D900D9">(TELEPHONE RINGING)</font>

12:59.697 --> 13:00.698
Hello?

13:00.864 --> 13:03.492
<i>Hey, Simon.
Franck wants to see you.</i>

13:13.210 --> 13:14.253
<font color="#D900D9">(MAN SCREAMING)</font>

13:21.677 --> 13:23.387
Where is it?

13:24.054 --> 13:27.683
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font> I don't know.
I'm sorry, Franck.

13:27.808 --> 13:31.020
You must have taken it. You
must have put it somewhere.

13:31.145 --> 13:32.896
Yeah, I must have.
I know I...

13:32.980 --> 13:34.690
Well, did you or did you not?

13:34.982 --> 13:37.651
I can't remember!
I got hit on the head!

13:37.735 --> 13:39.320
That you remember?

13:39.403 --> 13:43.407
Yeah, I got a big fucking scar on
my head to remind me, don't I?

13:43.574 --> 13:45.576
What did you expect?

13:45.743 --> 13:49.830
You assaulted me. I had a shotgun.
Simon, the plan was simple.

13:49.913 --> 13:53.751
All you needed to do was take the
painting and bring it to me.

13:53.917 --> 13:55.502
I know, I...

13:55.878 --> 13:58.255
So, where is it?

13:59.214 --> 14:02.092
I don't know, I can't remember.
I can't remember.

14:02.259 --> 14:04.678
I'm sorry, I can't remember.

14:04.762 --> 14:05.846
Franck!

14:05.929 --> 14:09.600
Amnesia's bollocks. Everyone
knows amnesia is bollocks.

14:09.767 --> 14:11.393
No, it's not.

14:11.477 --> 14:12.770
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMING)</font>

14:18.025 --> 14:19.193
<font color="#D900D9">(SCOOTER ENGINE REVS)</font>

14:30.954 --> 14:32.706
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> It's not
going to work.

14:33.957 --> 14:37.086
<font color="#808080">NATE:</font> What do you mean?<font color="#808080">
FRANCK:</font> He cannot remember.

14:37.669 --> 14:39.421
<font color="#808080">NATE:</font> How did you
work that out?

14:39.838 --> 14:43.842
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> Look at him. Any man who
knew would have told you by now.

14:49.848 --> 14:51.475
Hey. <font color="#D900D9">(WHISTLES)</font>

14:54.520 --> 14:56.188
You know what?

14:57.773 --> 14:59.691
I ought to kill you.

15:00.192 --> 15:01.777
Why don't you?

15:02.694 --> 15:06.031
Finish the job and put
me out of my misery.

15:06.532 --> 15:08.117
And then...

15:08.534 --> 15:11.453
...you can find your
own fucking painting.

15:16.041 --> 15:17.042
Riz.

15:18.502 --> 15:20.254
Give him some food.

15:21.505 --> 15:23.424
<font color="#808080">SURGEON:</font> <i>Well, his brain
is intact on a gross level.</i>

15:23.507 --> 15:26.343
<i>On a smaller scale,
who's to say?</i>

15:26.468 --> 15:27.761
What I'm saying
is we don't know.

15:27.845 --> 15:29.179
The memories may come
back, they may not.

15:29.304 --> 15:31.140
All you can do is wait and see.

15:31.515 --> 15:32.795
Isn't there something
you can do?

15:32.850 --> 15:35.102
For memory?
Nothing. Except time.

15:35.227 --> 15:37.062
Some sort of medicine?

15:37.438 --> 15:39.940
There's no drug
therapy for amnesia.

15:40.023 --> 15:42.443
What about other
sorts of therapy?

15:44.194 --> 15:45.237
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> Here.

15:45.988 --> 15:47.197
Pick one.
<font color="#D900D9">(SIMON INHALES)</font> Ow!

15:53.537 --> 15:55.789
Hypnosis? <font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

15:55.998 --> 15:58.208
He said it might work.

15:59.334 --> 16:03.088
What am I gonna tell him? I stole
a painting and now I've lost it?

16:03.213 --> 16:04.715
You know,
you make something up.

16:05.048 --> 16:06.425
What if that doesn't work?

16:06.842 --> 16:08.343
Doesn't work?

16:09.094 --> 16:10.095
Simon...

16:11.388 --> 16:13.056
Doesn't work?!

16:14.391 --> 16:16.059
Okay, okay.

16:21.023 --> 16:22.024
Um...

16:25.903 --> 16:27.404
That one.

16:28.530 --> 16:31.074
Why her? I don't know.
I like the name.

16:33.076 --> 16:34.161
Right.

16:37.748 --> 16:41.835
You walk across
a wide open space.

16:41.919 --> 16:46.173
Exactly the sort of place which
might once have made you panic.

16:46.256 --> 16:51.011
You are in Cape Canaveral and you
are Head of Mission Control.

16:51.094 --> 16:54.890
The rocket is ready to launch
and although you are excited...

16:55.015 --> 16:57.768
...you will not prematurely
release the rocket.

16:57.893 --> 17:01.271
And now you watch as the
spider leaves its web...

17:01.438 --> 17:04.775
...and crawls slowly across
the floor towards you.

17:04.900 --> 17:08.779
There is 30,000 feet of air
between you and the ground...

17:08.862 --> 17:12.031
...and the sound of those perfectly
functioning jet engines...

17:12.115 --> 17:15.285
...is making you feel calm
because you know...

17:15.410 --> 17:17.371
...that you are not hungry...

17:18.454 --> 17:22.251
...and that these are feelings
of stress and loneliness...

17:22.626 --> 17:24.962
...and that you will see
the ball cross the green

17:25.045 --> 17:27.464
and disappear into the hole.

17:38.767 --> 17:43.480
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> Um, okay, um, my name is not Simon Newton.
My name is David Maxwell.

17:43.647 --> 17:46.316
Uh, I cannot find my car keys.
<font color="#D900D9">(THUMPING)</font>

17:46.441 --> 17:49.319
Please stop doing that. Stop hitting it.
Say your name.

17:49.444 --> 17:50.487
Okay.

17:50.529 --> 17:52.698
My name is David Maxwell.
Yeah, set.

17:53.907 --> 17:56.076
Seriously,
what if I say too much?

17:56.201 --> 17:57.869
We wake you up.
<font color="#D900D9">(LOUD RINGTONE)</font>

18:17.180 --> 18:19.057
<font color="#D900D9">(FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)</font>

18:20.142 --> 18:21.810
<i>Mr. Maxwell?</i>

18:23.353 --> 18:25.022
<i>Mr. Maxwell?</i>

18:27.399 --> 18:30.819
<i>Mr. Maxwell?</i> <font color="#808080">
SIMON:</font> <i>That's me. I'm sorry.</i>

18:35.657 --> 18:37.326
Something the matter?

18:37.451 --> 18:39.036
Of course not.

18:39.161 --> 18:42.331
I'm Elizabeth Lamb.
I'm... Mr. Maxwell.

18:42.539 --> 18:43.540
Please.

18:43.624 --> 18:44.625
Okay.

18:49.087 --> 18:51.715
<font color="#D900D9">(ELIZABETH OVER HEADPHONES)</font>
<i>You've come to find your car keys?</i>

18:51.840 --> 18:52.841
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> <i>Yep.</i>

18:52.924 --> 18:54.593
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>
They're just in here.</i>

18:55.093 --> 18:56.094
<font color="#D900D9">(SIMON CHUCKLES)</font>

18:56.678 --> 18:59.139
I wish.
Hang up your coat.

18:59.264 --> 19:00.682
Have a seat.

19:04.978 --> 19:07.814
Have you ever been
hypnotized before?

19:07.939 --> 19:10.359
No. Um...

19:12.944 --> 19:16.239
No. No, at least not
that I can remember.

19:16.990 --> 19:18.700
I suppose you've
spent some time

19:18.784 --> 19:21.161
trying to remember where
you put these keys?

19:21.286 --> 19:24.623
I've tried everything. I just keep
coming up against a brick wall.

19:24.748 --> 19:26.958
Of course. So...

19:27.084 --> 19:30.754
...I don't want you
to do the work today.

19:31.755 --> 19:34.675
I want you... to sit back.

19:40.389 --> 19:42.891
And I want you
to close your eyes.

19:43.392 --> 19:45.227
We're starting, right.

19:45.644 --> 19:48.313
I want you to think
about someone else.

19:49.022 --> 19:51.274
Someone who could
do it for you.

19:51.400 --> 19:53.151
<i>Another man.</i>

19:53.777 --> 19:56.196
<i>Like you but not you.</i>

19:57.280 --> 20:00.617
I want you to focus on him.
Let him take over.

20:02.160 --> 20:03.829
<i>Is he there?</i>

20:05.122 --> 20:07.040
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> <i>Yes.</i>
Is he under already?

20:07.165 --> 20:09.084
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>Do you wanna
give him a name?</i>

20:09.418 --> 20:10.460
Simon.

20:10.585 --> 20:12.003
<i>Simon Newton.</i>

20:12.129 --> 20:14.131
Get him out of there.
No, no.

20:14.923 --> 20:17.926
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>Right, Simon.
Welcome to the session.</i>

20:18.218 --> 20:21.555
Thanks. It's really
nice to be here.

20:24.891 --> 20:27.352
Now I want you to relax, Simon.

20:28.562 --> 20:30.564
I like your voice.

20:32.441 --> 20:35.110
And now your mind
is starting to think.

20:35.819 --> 20:40.824
So think about those keys. And you
now can feel them in your hand.

20:42.200 --> 20:45.412
The shape. The metal.

20:45.996 --> 20:48.081
And you can see the color.

20:49.082 --> 20:50.167
Blue.

20:51.334 --> 20:53.920
They are on a blue key-ring.

20:54.337 --> 20:56.047
And your mind
starts to think about

20:56.131 --> 20:58.550
the last time
you remember them.

21:01.052 --> 21:03.054
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> <i>I'm trying to walk...</i>

21:06.141 --> 21:07.559
<i>...and they're in my pocket.</i>

21:07.642 --> 21:10.312
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>And I want you to
picture them in your pocket...</i>

21:10.437 --> 21:14.399
<i>...exactly as they were
before you lifted them out...</i>

21:15.275 --> 21:17.277
...and you
placed them somewhere.

21:17.903 --> 21:19.571
A safe place...

21:20.197 --> 21:21.531
<i>...that, when
the time is right,</i>

21:21.615 --> 21:24.785
<i>you will be able to reach for
them and they will be there.</i>

21:25.994 --> 21:27.871
Where did you say they were?

21:30.207 --> 21:31.750
In the wardrobe.

21:38.381 --> 21:40.383
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>What's in
the wardrobe, Simon?</i>

21:41.343 --> 21:42.636
The...

21:43.720 --> 21:45.222
<font color="#D900D9">(LOUD RINGTONE)</font>

21:48.475 --> 21:50.227
I'm sorry about that.

21:50.602 --> 21:52.229
Was I hypnotized?

21:53.939 --> 21:56.608
No, you were just
finding your car keys.

21:59.528 --> 22:00.821
<font color="#D900D9">(CLATTERING)</font>

22:00.904 --> 22:03.031
<font color="#D900D9">(MEN GRUMBLING)</font>
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

22:04.241 --> 22:06.076
<font color="#808080">DOMINIC:</font> Let me fucking
get in through there.

22:14.209 --> 22:18.755
Really sorry. I kept thinking about the painting.
She just kept saying "keys".

22:18.880 --> 22:21.174
Well, that's it, then,
it can't be done.

22:22.092 --> 22:25.011
She got his name in 30 seconds.

22:25.220 --> 22:27.264
And she found the car keys.

22:27.389 --> 22:29.683
Whatever is in his head,
she can find.

22:29.808 --> 22:31.935
What am I supposed to say,
that I lost my keys again?

22:32.060 --> 22:34.688
You're the clever boy.
You got us into this

22:34.771 --> 22:36.731
so now you think of
something to get us out.

22:38.567 --> 22:40.318
And you make it work.

22:43.572 --> 22:44.573
<font color="#D900D9">(DOOR SLAMS)</font>

22:45.782 --> 22:47.450
<font color="#D900D9">(BREATHING HEAVILY)</font>

22:49.369 --> 22:50.537
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font>

23:07.095 --> 23:08.471
<font color="#D900D9">(INDISTINCT)</font>

23:15.520 --> 23:17.272
<font color="#D900D9">(TIRES SCREECH)</font><font color="#808080">
CYCLIST:</font> Hey! Fucking pedestrians!

23:17.355 --> 23:18.356
Hey!

23:22.319 --> 23:23.570
St. Pancras please.

23:59.397 --> 24:01.816
You must think
I'm stalking you.

24:02.359 --> 24:06.112
No, I just think you've put
yourself under a lot of pressure.

24:08.823 --> 24:11.409
To be honest, I'm not
here to look for my keys.

24:11.493 --> 24:12.869
I found them, thank you.

24:12.994 --> 24:15.497
I'm looking for
something a bit more...

24:16.373 --> 24:18.917
...personal. And...

24:19.042 --> 24:21.169
...I can't tell
you what it is.

24:21.294 --> 24:23.797
It's not porn.
I promise.

24:23.922 --> 24:26.925
<i>And I just really
need to find this thing.</i>

24:27.050 --> 24:29.803
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>Hypnosis
is the perfect tool.</i>

24:29.886 --> 24:31.221
<i>I don't need to know
what it is.</i>

24:37.310 --> 24:40.021
<font color="#D900D9">(ELIZABETH ON STEREO)</font>
<i>So I'd like you to close your eyes</i>

24:40.105 --> 24:41.982
<i>and imagine
you're in an elevator.</i>

24:43.024 --> 24:46.736
<i>A wide elevator with velvet
walls and thick carpets.</i>

24:46.861 --> 24:49.114
<i>And as the doors close...</i>

24:49.239 --> 24:51.783
<i>your eyelids become heavier.</i>

24:52.575 --> 24:54.786
<i>And as your eyes become heavier</i>

24:54.869 --> 24:57.163
<i>and the elevator
begins to go down...</i>

24:57.956 --> 25:01.710
<i>...you realize that this is
the elevator of relaxation.</i>

25:03.461 --> 25:07.507
<i>And now you're on the
third floor going down...</i>

25:07.632 --> 25:11.177
<i>...and you could get out
but you want to go on...</i>

25:11.970 --> 25:13.263
...deeper.

25:13.346 --> 25:14.472
<i>Deeper.</i>

25:15.974 --> 25:18.560
<i>Deeper into relaxation.</i>

25:20.562 --> 25:24.482
<i>And you feel that perhaps
you'll never want to get out.</i>

25:24.607 --> 25:26.776
<i>It's so safe here.</i>

25:26.943 --> 25:28.319
<i>So comfortable.</i>

25:29.279 --> 25:31.031
<i>So relaxed.</i>

25:32.782 --> 25:35.660
I don't wanna talk
to Simon anymore.

25:35.785 --> 25:40.040
I wanna talk to the men who are listening.
The men who hurt him.

25:40.165 --> 25:41.791
Oh, fuck.

25:57.140 --> 25:58.516
<font color="#D900D9">(COUGHING)</font>

26:01.686 --> 26:02.812
<font color="#D900D9">(EXHALES)</font>

26:07.776 --> 26:09.027
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font>

26:12.322 --> 26:13.907
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> <i>You feel safe?</i>

26:15.825 --> 26:18.203
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>Safe?</i> <font color="#808080">
FRANCK:</font> <i>Yes.</i>

26:20.663 --> 26:22.832
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>I don't think
you'll hurt me.</i>

26:23.750 --> 26:25.710
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> <i>You're right.
Absolutely.</i>

26:25.835 --> 26:27.115
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> <i>It would be irrational.</i>

26:27.170 --> 26:30.507
<i>And yet we are
like that, aren't we?</i>

26:31.174 --> 26:34.511
<i>All of us sometimes stupid.
Irrational.</i>

26:35.678 --> 26:38.848
<i>It's fear, I think.
Fear of the unknown.</i>

26:41.184 --> 26:44.270
<i>There are four of us
but we are frightened of you.</i>

26:46.189 --> 26:48.024
You don't need to be.

26:48.608 --> 26:50.610
I'm so glad to hear that.

26:53.363 --> 26:55.615
Simon is an unusual subject.

26:56.074 --> 26:59.702
He floats in and out
of trance very easily.

27:00.120 --> 27:01.121
But...

27:01.871 --> 27:03.873
...he's got
a lot on his mind.

27:04.290 --> 27:06.876
Fear. Resentment. Anger.

27:08.419 --> 27:10.421
Why do you think he did it?

27:11.089 --> 27:12.674
Greed, most likely.

27:12.757 --> 27:14.551
Does he strike you as greedy?

27:14.634 --> 27:17.137
Everyone is...
sooner or later.

27:17.971 --> 27:21.057
Simon wanted the painting,
that's it.

27:21.224 --> 27:22.725
For himself?

27:22.892 --> 27:25.728
Well, it's not like
he did it for someone else.

27:25.895 --> 27:27.480
Quite sure of that, are you?

27:28.231 --> 27:29.816
Please don't.

27:32.652 --> 27:34.904
So, can you do it?

27:35.405 --> 27:37.407
Hypnotherapy will work.

27:37.615 --> 27:38.616
But?

27:40.410 --> 27:43.079
Only if it's a partnership.

27:43.413 --> 27:44.956
Very well.

27:45.248 --> 27:47.625
The finder's fee is 3%.

27:47.750 --> 27:49.419
It's not enough.

27:50.253 --> 27:51.838
See what I mean?

27:52.589 --> 27:57.260
It's not about the money. I have to
have equal status in the group...

27:57.343 --> 27:59.762
...otherwise Simon
won't respect me.

28:03.433 --> 28:05.351
If you wanna make progress...

28:06.102 --> 28:07.187
...you really
have to move beyond

28:07.270 --> 28:09.856
getting one over
on people, Franck.

28:14.861 --> 28:17.447
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> Hypnotherapy
is a means of altering

28:17.530 --> 28:19.616
unwanted or
dysfunctional behavior.

28:19.699 --> 28:22.660
The unwanted behavior
in Simon's case is forgetting.

28:22.785 --> 28:24.204
<font color="#808080">DOMINIC:</font> You mean
he's doing it deliberately?

28:24.287 --> 28:26.706
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> Not in the sense
that you mean, Dominic.

28:26.831 --> 28:28.291
We keep secrets from
lots of people,

28:28.374 --> 28:30.460
but most of all we keep
them from ourselves.

28:30.543 --> 28:32.879
And we call that forgetting.
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font>

28:35.965 --> 28:38.468
Now, Simon...

28:40.720 --> 28:42.722
...I'd like you
to close your eyes.

28:46.476 --> 28:48.061
Okay, okay.
<font color="#D900D9">(CLEARS THROAT)</font>

28:49.979 --> 28:52.649
I'd like you to think
about being at home.

28:53.358 --> 28:57.028
Home is a place
where you feel secure.

28:58.071 --> 28:59.656
In control.

29:01.908 --> 29:05.578
You are feeling
refreshed and positive.

29:05.662 --> 29:07.455
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING DEEPLY)</font>

29:09.499 --> 29:11.876
<i>And when the doorbell rings...</i>
<font color="#D900D9">(RINGING)</font>

29:12.543 --> 29:14.879
<i>...you feel
a rush of enthusiasm.</i>

29:15.004 --> 29:17.882
Hello?
<i>Parcel for Simon Newton, please.</i>

29:18.675 --> 29:21.094
Er... coming.

29:25.390 --> 29:28.726
<i>Hey, Mr. Postman.
Thank you very much.</i>

29:29.060 --> 29:31.521
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>You are excited...</i>

29:34.274 --> 29:36.276
<i>...but you stay calm...</i>

29:37.443 --> 29:40.780
<i>...because you know that
this is no ordinary package.</i>

29:41.531 --> 29:43.783
<i>Inside this package...</i>

29:44.742 --> 29:47.620
...is the memory that
you have been waiting for.

29:47.704 --> 29:49.956
And you know that
when you open it up

29:50.039 --> 29:52.292
you will find what
you did that day...

29:53.126 --> 29:55.712
...what you did with the painting.
And now...

29:56.129 --> 29:57.880
...taking your time...

29:58.548 --> 30:00.216
...you open it.

30:03.553 --> 30:04.762
<font color="#D900D9">(EXHALES)</font>

30:05.722 --> 30:08.141
Now you're not going to rush...

30:10.059 --> 30:13.730
...because it's a big step
even to have got this far.

30:15.815 --> 30:17.150
Slowly...

30:18.818 --> 30:21.404
...so as not to
upset the contents...

30:22.071 --> 30:23.489
...you open it.

30:47.889 --> 30:48.890
<font color="#D900D9">(GRUNTS)</font>

30:51.934 --> 30:53.519
<font color="#D900D9">(INHALES SHARPLY)</font>

30:59.650 --> 31:01.486
<font color="#D900D9">(DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES)</font>

31:02.278 --> 31:04.447
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> Franck. May I?
Yeah.

31:21.339 --> 31:22.965
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> Are you okay?

31:23.383 --> 31:24.384
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> Fine.

31:26.302 --> 31:28.137
How did you meet them?

31:28.221 --> 31:29.222
Riz...

31:30.723 --> 31:32.725
...I used to buy
drugs from Riz.

31:33.351 --> 31:37.313
That was it really. Well, the
thing is, I needed money.

31:37.397 --> 31:38.523
What for?

31:38.981 --> 31:40.650
Gambling debt.

31:41.401 --> 31:43.694
I was... I am...

31:43.778 --> 31:44.779
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHING)</font>

31:44.862 --> 31:46.197
...addicted...

31:48.991 --> 31:50.368
...to gambling.

31:54.914 --> 31:57.750
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font> I was really
good at it, you know.

32:02.755 --> 32:04.924
<i>I wasn't quite
good enough, though.</i>

32:05.049 --> 32:07.760
<i>And not really good enough
isn't really good at all.</i>

32:07.885 --> 32:09.595
<i>Not at that level.</i>

32:09.720 --> 32:13.349
I tried to give it up. I tried
everything I could to kick it.

32:13.683 --> 32:16.436
I should have tried hypnotism.
You should.

32:16.561 --> 32:18.187
Maybe next time?

32:19.021 --> 32:21.858
<i>Anyway, I did what
all bad gamblers do...</i>

32:22.024 --> 32:26.112
<i>...I borrowed more and played for
higher and higher stakes hoping...</i>

32:26.237 --> 32:28.114
<i>...that my luck would change.</i>

32:28.239 --> 32:29.699
And when that didn't happen...

32:32.368 --> 32:33.911
<i>...I panicked.</i>

32:36.956 --> 32:38.708
<i>To various people...</i>

32:39.375 --> 32:44.297
...in various ways I am in
for money I don't have.

32:44.922 --> 32:45.923
Never will.

32:47.133 --> 32:49.135
<i>This painting came in.</i>

32:49.260 --> 32:52.555
This fucking painting.<font color="#808080">
FRANCIS:</font> <i>Are you a gambling man, Simon?</i>

32:54.056 --> 32:56.976
Because I'll wager you,
anything you care to name...

32:57.101 --> 33:00.605
...that I can flog this in the
autumn sale for over 25 million.

33:00.730 --> 33:02.064
Sterling.

33:03.524 --> 33:06.319
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> <i>And I know it sounds
ridiculous, an inside job,</i>

33:06.402 --> 33:08.237
<i>but it just seemed
like the answer.</i>

33:08.362 --> 33:12.617
I didn't know any criminals so I
thought Riz might. He brought me here.

33:16.829 --> 33:18.748
<i>He introduced me to Franck.</i>

33:18.873 --> 33:20.416
<font color="#D900D9">(YELLING IN FRENCH)</font>

33:25.630 --> 33:30.009
<i>Franck cleared my debt
in return for the painting.</i>

33:31.052 --> 33:33.721
<i>I owe him a lot of money.</i>

33:35.097 --> 33:38.684
And I don't know
what I'm going to do.

33:40.811 --> 33:43.439
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>He's afraid that once
he's remembered, you'll kill him.</i>

33:43.564 --> 33:45.566
<font color="#808080">DOMINIC:</font> <i>That's ridiculous.</i> <font color="#808080">
ELIZABETH:</font> <i>Is it?</i>

33:47.109 --> 33:49.654
Let's talk about killing. Have
you ever killed anyone, Dominic?

33:49.737 --> 33:50.780
No.

33:51.072 --> 33:54.242
Well, yeah, in Iraq.
Loads, obviously.

33:54.408 --> 33:55.648
But that's artillery, isn't it?

33:55.701 --> 33:57.828
You never get to see
exactly who you've...

33:57.954 --> 33:58.955
Nate.

33:59.956 --> 34:02.959
Killed anyone?
Define 'killed'.

34:03.584 --> 34:06.337
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font><font color="#808080"> ELIZABETH:</font> That's
exactly why he won't open up.

34:06.462 --> 34:10.341
His behavior isn't dysfunctional,
it's entirely logical.

34:10.466 --> 34:12.927
It's straightforward
self-preservation.

34:13.553 --> 34:16.806
Why do you think he cheated
you in the first place?

34:17.139 --> 34:18.933
So what do you suggest?

34:19.266 --> 34:21.978
How do we make him
feel more secure?

34:22.103 --> 34:24.522
In an ideal world
he'd kill you all.

34:25.398 --> 34:27.315
That would do it, right?
Ideal.

34:27.440 --> 34:29.025
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> Most likely.

34:29.485 --> 34:34.156
Okay. But supposing, for the sake
of argument, we don't go for that.

34:34.614 --> 34:35.616
Then what?

34:36.324 --> 34:39.078
He needs to see you
weak and exposed

34:39.161 --> 34:40.788
to whatever it is
you fear the most.

34:40.955 --> 34:43.291
Nonsense.
Not gonna happen.

34:43.416 --> 34:45.293
He needs to know
that you're vulnerable.

34:45.418 --> 34:47.753
If you're suggesting what I think...
I'm a professional.

34:47.878 --> 34:49.589
I'm not going to
put you on the stage.

34:49.672 --> 34:52.675
The answer is definitely 'no'.

34:53.592 --> 34:57.805
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> Now the next voice
you hear... will be Simon's.

34:57.930 --> 35:01.309
And he is going to say the word
that I have prepared for you.

35:01.434 --> 35:03.978
And when he speaks that word...

35:04.103 --> 35:07.898
...you will descend into your
very own world of fear...

35:08.190 --> 35:11.944
...from which only
he can bring you back.

35:23.331 --> 35:24.624
Strawberry.

35:25.082 --> 35:26.667
<font color="#D900D9">(NATE GROANS)</font>
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

35:31.088 --> 35:32.632
<font color="#D900D9">(ALL CHUCKLING)</font>

35:38.220 --> 35:39.889
<font color="#D900D9">(NATE CONTINUES GROANING)</font>

35:46.228 --> 35:47.229
<font color="#D900D9">(YELLING)</font>

35:53.069 --> 35:54.362
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMS)</font>

35:56.572 --> 35:57.573
Simon.

36:00.159 --> 36:01.452
<font color="#D900D9">(NATE GROANING)</font>

36:02.745 --> 36:03.746
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMING)</font>

36:05.873 --> 36:07.750
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> Simon, say it!

36:07.917 --> 36:09.251
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> Strawberry.

36:12.963 --> 36:14.423
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHING)</font>

36:16.592 --> 36:18.678
That was incredible.

36:20.596 --> 36:22.181
Are you all right?

36:22.264 --> 36:23.599
Yeah. Why?

36:23.683 --> 36:25.810
<font color="#D900D9">(CONTINUES LAUGHING)</font>

36:25.893 --> 36:27.895
He doesn't know.

36:29.355 --> 36:31.065
Oh, I'm sorry, man.

36:38.531 --> 36:39.990
<font color="#D900D9">(ELEVATOR BELL DINGS)</font>

36:57.174 --> 36:58.676
<font color="#D900D9">(TAP RUNNING)</font>

37:03.973 --> 37:05.307
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING)</font>

37:06.600 --> 37:08.602
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> Shall I
scrub your back?

37:12.648 --> 37:14.483
How did you...?

37:14.608 --> 37:16.610
Well, I used to...

37:17.486 --> 37:18.654
...I used to, you know...

37:21.407 --> 37:22.450
So...

37:24.493 --> 37:28.664
...we got enough, I think,
to make our boy feel secure.

37:28.789 --> 37:30.916
Safe to remember, all that.
I think so.

37:31.417 --> 37:34.253
Now we progress.
I like that, it's good.

37:34.378 --> 37:36.338
Soon we'll have the painting.

37:37.256 --> 37:39.258
And what about poor old Nate?

37:39.383 --> 37:42.845
Does he still fall to pieces at
every mention of the little berry?

37:44.180 --> 37:48.851
No. Sustained post hypnotic
suggestion is more difficult.

37:49.685 --> 37:52.354
More difficult,
but you can do it, right?

37:53.355 --> 37:55.357
Not to everyone, of course.

37:55.858 --> 38:00.529
5%? Correct me if I'm wrong.
5% of the population?

38:00.613 --> 38:04.366
Yes. Can be described
as extremely suggestible.

38:04.700 --> 38:06.535
Wow, 5%.

38:07.244 --> 38:08.704
Who'd have thought?

38:09.413 --> 38:12.249
And what can you make them do?
<font color="#D900D9">(SCOFFS)</font>

38:13.250 --> 38:15.961
Well, I'm just asking.
I'm interested.

38:20.049 --> 38:21.634
All right.

38:22.384 --> 38:26.722
Well, let's see, if you
had the right person...

38:27.890 --> 38:31.101
...if you get a hold
of them, dig right in...

38:31.393 --> 38:33.938
...if you get them
under your spell...

38:35.439 --> 38:39.735
...if you work hard
...and take your time...

38:41.487 --> 38:43.239
...and do it right...

38:45.491 --> 38:48.118
...you can make
them want to do...

38:48.786 --> 38:50.120
...almost...

38:51.247 --> 38:52.581
...anything.

39:01.757 --> 39:03.425
<font color="#D900D9">(SPEAKS FRENCH)</font>

39:05.135 --> 39:06.512
<font color="#D900D9">(WHISTLING)</font>

39:10.891 --> 39:12.768
<font color="#D900D9">(<i>CHANSON D'AMOUR</i>
BY ART AND DOTTY TODD PLAYING)</font>

39:29.159 --> 39:30.828
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>There you are...</i>

39:31.287 --> 39:33.122
<i>...in an open-top car...</i>

39:33.205 --> 39:37.209
<i>...driving through the French countryside
with a beautiful young woman.</i>

39:37.334 --> 39:40.462
<i>And the radio plays
some forgotten song...</i>

39:40.546 --> 39:45.217
...and the sun burns the back of
your heads in the warm wind...

39:45.801 --> 39:48.470
<i>...and with
every mile you travel...</i>

39:49.471 --> 39:53.475
<i>...all your problems seem so
far away and so long ago.</i>

39:59.481 --> 40:04.737
<i>And soon a field of sunflowers
gives way to a low building...</i>

40:04.862 --> 40:07.031
<i>...of stone and tile.</i>

40:07.156 --> 40:09.742
<i>The girl's dress, her calves...</i>

40:10.159 --> 40:15.205
<i>...leads you through a corridor
to a vast room of paintings.</i>

40:15.331 --> 40:17.583
Caravaggio's 'Adoration'.

40:22.713 --> 40:24.048
Cezanne.

40:27.051 --> 40:28.886
Vermeer's 'Concert'.

40:30.554 --> 40:31.680
Van Gogh.

40:33.557 --> 40:34.892
Modigliani.

40:36.894 --> 40:39.063
Manet. Degas.

40:42.566 --> 40:44.401
And Rembrandt himself.

40:45.027 --> 40:46.195
<font color="#D900D9">(GASPING)</font>

40:52.534 --> 40:55.120
'The Storm On
The Sea Of Galilee'.

40:55.954 --> 40:58.707
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> These are
the lost paintings...

40:59.375 --> 41:03.921
...all the stolen and
destroyed, but now together...

41:04.046 --> 41:06.715
...authenticated, safe.

41:08.550 --> 41:12.137
<i>She takes your hand and leads
you into a final room.</i>

41:18.560 --> 41:20.229
<i>And it's in here...</i>

41:21.563 --> 41:23.899
<i>...in this
magical safe place...</i>

41:25.067 --> 41:27.069
<i>...that you feel ready.</i>

41:27.444 --> 41:29.947
<i>And you reach
into the package...</i>

41:31.156 --> 41:33.409
<i>...and you lift
out your memory.</i>

41:33.742 --> 41:37.746
<i>The memory of what happened that day.
The memory of what you did.</i>

41:39.790 --> 41:41.250
And now...

41:41.375 --> 41:43.919
...safe and relaxed...

41:44.044 --> 41:45.963
...you decide to watch.

41:47.131 --> 41:49.174
You decide to remember.

41:50.634 --> 41:53.721
<i>...fifty thousand pounds.</i>

41:57.433 --> 41:59.309
<i>Sold to paddle 88.</i>

41:59.810 --> 42:02.104
I remember that day.

42:03.480 --> 42:06.108
<i>I remember.
I take the painting.</i>

42:08.819 --> 42:10.988
<i>I carry it in front of me.</i>
<font color="#D900D9">(ALARM BLARING)</font>

42:14.450 --> 42:17.661
<i>And I cut the canvas free with
a razor blade.</i> <font color="#D900D9">(INDISTINCT)</font>

42:21.957 --> 42:24.418
<i>I conceal the painting.</i>

42:26.128 --> 42:27.838
I carry on.
Remember...

42:27.963 --> 42:30.841
...no piece of art is worth a human life.
Sound advice that.

42:30.966 --> 42:33.135
And I try to remember it.
You see if you can.

42:33.302 --> 42:35.137
<i>I discard the razor blade.</i>

42:35.262 --> 42:38.265
We are to take the most
valuable item, or items,

42:38.348 --> 42:39.683
to a place of safe...

42:39.808 --> 42:41.769
Franck?!
Stay back.

42:44.688 --> 42:46.190
Put it down.

42:52.946 --> 42:54.156
Simon...

42:54.323 --> 42:55.657
<i>He's about to look.</i>

42:57.659 --> 42:58.660
I can't let him.

42:58.869 --> 43:00.190
<font color="#D900D9">(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)</font>
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

43:02.539 --> 43:03.707
<font color="#D900D9">(EXHALES)</font>

43:07.127 --> 43:08.128
Don't.
<font color="#D900D9">(ALARM BLARING)</font>

43:08.587 --> 43:09.588
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

43:14.343 --> 43:16.136
From a safe distance...

43:16.887 --> 43:19.181
...you see that
you have been hit.

43:21.642 --> 43:22.684
<font color="#D900D9">(MUFFLED)</font> Simon?!

43:24.311 --> 43:25.646
Simon!

43:25.729 --> 43:28.357
But you continue to watch.

43:29.358 --> 43:31.693
You continue to remember.

43:35.197 --> 43:36.865
<font color="#D900D9">(ALARM BLARING)</font>

43:43.163 --> 43:44.540
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING SOFTLY)</font>

43:46.166 --> 43:47.334
I still have it.

43:49.753 --> 43:52.422
I wake up and I still
have the painting.

43:55.759 --> 43:58.220
<i>I get up and I go outside.
There's a noise.</i>

43:58.595 --> 44:02.599
<i>I have to walk away. I cannot stay
here, not with this painting.</i>

44:02.724 --> 44:06.728
I feel my heart vibrating.

44:07.646 --> 44:08.856
<font color="#D900D9">(CELL PHONE BUZZING)</font>

44:08.939 --> 44:12.067
<i>My phone vibrating.</i>

44:12.860 --> 44:14.903
I look at it.

44:14.987 --> 44:16.071
<font color="#D900D9">(TIRES SCREECHING)</font>

44:19.241 --> 44:23.203
<font color="#D900D9">(GASPING)</font>
<i>The car nearly kills me.</i>

44:23.328 --> 44:25.539
She's in the car.

44:25.831 --> 44:26.915
Who is?

44:28.917 --> 44:30.377
You are!

44:33.005 --> 44:34.882
Oh my God.
Are you all right?

44:35.173 --> 44:36.425
Elizabeth?

44:36.550 --> 44:39.928
I'm not Elizabeth.
Shall I call an ambulance?

44:40.095 --> 44:41.513
I remember.

44:41.597 --> 44:44.057
<font color="#D900D9">(SNAPS FINGERS)</font>
I remember everything.

44:44.224 --> 44:46.101
Look, why don't I
take you to hospital?

44:46.226 --> 44:47.227
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> <i>Yeah.</i>

44:52.107 --> 44:53.275
Elizabeth?
<font color="#D900D9">(SIREN WAILING)</font>

44:56.445 --> 44:59.573
Shall I help you with your seat belt?
Why did you lie to me?

45:00.282 --> 45:01.283
What?

45:01.575 --> 45:03.452
You made me forget.

45:09.207 --> 45:11.585
He's got it on him.
Look, he's got it on him.

45:11.710 --> 45:14.922
Okay, maybe I oughta just...
call for that ambulance.

45:15.923 --> 45:18.383
Open your jacket. Who called you?
<font color="#D900D9">(FRANCK SHUSHING)</font>

45:18.467 --> 45:20.218
I'm sorry. Will you
let me go, please?

45:20.302 --> 45:21.803
<font color="#808080">DOMINIC:</font> <i>Tell him
where you left it!</i>

45:21.970 --> 45:24.306
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font> <i>I don't
want you to go.</i>

45:24.473 --> 45:26.767
Never mind her!
Forget about her!

45:26.892 --> 45:28.560
Open his jacket!
<font color="#D900D9">(YELLING)</font>

45:32.147 --> 45:34.608
What are you gonna do
with the fucking painting?!

45:34.733 --> 45:36.485
Just get him to tell us
where he put it.

45:37.569 --> 45:39.571
Tell us where you left it!
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMING)</font>

45:53.919 --> 45:55.337
<font color="#D900D9">(SIMON PANTING)</font>

46:34.167 --> 46:35.877
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>Simon,
can you hear me?</i>

46:36.712 --> 46:38.213
Yes, I can hear you.

46:38.380 --> 46:40.674
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>Good.
Can you see the blue screen?</i>

46:40.799 --> 46:41.800
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> Yes.

46:43.552 --> 46:45.554
<i>I'm going to
show you some images...</i>

46:45.721 --> 46:49.975
...while we scan the response
generated in your brain by each one.

46:56.189 --> 46:58.400
<font color="#D900D9">(COFFEE PERCOLATOR BUBBLING)</font>

46:59.901 --> 47:02.904
<i>The images will continue to
run but you can override that</i>

47:02.988 --> 47:05.240
<i>by thinking
of a particular one.</i>

47:05.407 --> 47:07.367
<i>And every 10 seconds
the least chosen image</i>

47:07.451 --> 47:10.078
<i>will be discarded until
there is only one left.</i>

47:10.203 --> 47:12.414
<i>However, every time
you think of this one...</i>

47:14.041 --> 47:16.710
<i>you will receive
an electric shock.</i>

47:17.502 --> 47:20.922
<i>And the more you select it
the higher the voltage.</i>

47:21.506 --> 47:23.091
<i>Do you understand?</i>

47:23.258 --> 47:24.384
Yeah.

47:28.555 --> 47:29.556
Hello.

47:30.766 --> 47:34.102
I slept on the sofa.
I was worried about you.

47:34.978 --> 47:35.979
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

47:38.815 --> 47:40.650
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANS AND CHUCKLES)</font>

47:41.526 --> 47:43.445
I had this dream.

47:44.446 --> 47:46.239
Wasn't a dream.

47:52.537 --> 47:54.539
I am so...

47:54.915 --> 47:57.459
...so, so sorry.

47:58.210 --> 48:00.212
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>What is
a person, Franck?</i>

48:02.964 --> 48:04.299
Not my line of work.

48:04.716 --> 48:06.134
It's fine.

48:06.468 --> 48:09.137
Being obsessed with someone is fine?
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

48:09.262 --> 48:10.305
No.

48:10.806 --> 48:12.641
But to have feelings...

48:14.101 --> 48:15.143
...yes.

48:16.603 --> 48:18.105
What we are...

48:18.313 --> 48:22.818
...is the sum of everything we've
ever said, done and felt...

48:22.984 --> 48:25.403
...all wrapped up
in one unique thread

48:25.487 --> 48:27.864
which is constantly
being revised and remembered.

48:27.948 --> 48:29.157
<font color="#D900D9">(YELLS)</font>

48:29.324 --> 48:33.662
So to be yourself you have to
constantly remember yourself.

48:33.787 --> 48:36.373
It's a full-time job
but that's how it works.

48:36.498 --> 48:40.794
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font> When you hit him on
the head you broke the thread.

48:40.919 --> 48:42.504
He's fixing it...

48:42.671 --> 48:45.006
...with false memories,
with fantasies.

48:45.173 --> 48:47.592
There's a space to fill so...

48:48.593 --> 48:50.470
...he fills it with me.
<font color="#D900D9">(BEEPING)</font>

48:50.595 --> 48:52.681
He's in love with you?

48:52.848 --> 48:54.641
We call it transference.

48:54.724 --> 48:55.851
<font color="#D900D9">(CRIES OUT)</font>

48:56.601 --> 48:58.770
I don't know what to say...

48:59.813 --> 49:00.814
...now.

49:02.357 --> 49:04.818
Okay. But where is the painting?

49:05.110 --> 49:07.112
The same place
it's always been.

49:07.779 --> 49:09.865
Yes, but now
you are the problem.

49:10.031 --> 49:11.032
Yes.

49:11.950 --> 49:14.286
But I may also be the solution.

49:14.369 --> 49:17.372
When in doubt
...try something traditional.

49:19.666 --> 49:22.169
Traditional?
Okay. Right, how's this?

49:22.836 --> 49:24.379
How would you...

49:24.546 --> 49:28.133
...like to, with me,
go out somewhere?

49:28.717 --> 49:30.552
What, you're gonna
screw him, is that it?

49:30.677 --> 49:31.678
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANS)</font>

49:31.845 --> 49:34.514
You'll fuck him just to
get him to remember?

49:34.639 --> 49:37.726
It's not conventional practice,
but under the circumstances...

49:39.311 --> 49:40.729
Pick me up at 8.

49:40.812 --> 49:42.522
Where would you like to go?

49:42.689 --> 49:45.233
You choose.
I don't care.

49:45.567 --> 49:47.194
Coffee's on.

49:47.569 --> 49:48.570
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font>

49:51.489 --> 49:54.826
Okay, but you wear a wire.
Don't be ridiculous.

49:54.910 --> 49:55.911
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

50:01.082 --> 50:02.918
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> You can keep the rest.
Thanks, man.

50:03.043 --> 50:05.503
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> <i>I don't like the idea
of you being alone with him.</i>

50:05.587 --> 50:07.672
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>I'm not wild
about it myself, Franck.</i>

50:07.756 --> 50:11.426
So if you can see any other way
to deal with this obsession...

50:11.885 --> 50:13.678
...I'd love to hear it.

50:23.104 --> 50:24.105
<font color="#D900D9">(BEEPS)</font>

50:30.946 --> 50:33.907
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> I'm glad I had you
choose the place. It's nice.

50:34.032 --> 50:36.618
It is. I haven't
been here in a while.

50:36.785 --> 50:38.453
Thank you very much.

50:38.578 --> 50:41.456
So what do you recommend? I...

50:42.916 --> 50:45.961
...usually have the steak,
which is a lie.

50:47.629 --> 50:49.965
I don't usually
have the steak. I...

50:50.590 --> 50:52.467
...I've never
been here before.

50:52.592 --> 50:54.970
Simon. You need therapy.

50:56.388 --> 50:59.140
I've been feeling
a little confused lately.

50:59.808 --> 51:01.977
I just imagined
I'd been here before.

51:02.102 --> 51:04.980
I could have sworn that
I'd met that waiter before.

51:05.063 --> 51:06.064
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

51:07.315 --> 51:10.819
And then what happens?
I give him what he wants...

51:11.444 --> 51:12.988
<i>...he's mine.</i>

51:13.655 --> 51:16.324
<i>And after that,
he gives me what I want...</i>

51:17.242 --> 51:20.328
...what we want.
Just like that?

51:21.079 --> 51:25.250
He isn't really receiving
electric shocks. <font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

51:25.834 --> 51:26.835
<font color="#D900D9">(TAPPING ON GLASS)</font>

51:28.837 --> 51:30.755
He only believes he is.

51:52.527 --> 51:55.864
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> <i>Just here. If you just pull
in here on the left, thank you.</i>

51:57.032 --> 51:59.492
This is, this is me, actually.

52:00.535 --> 52:01.536
Okay?

52:03.371 --> 52:05.373
It's all right.
Okay. Have a good night.

52:16.843 --> 52:19.179
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>There's a problem.
He's jealous.</i>

52:19.262 --> 52:20.263
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> <i>Jealous?</i>

52:21.056 --> 52:22.807
Of me? That's so cute.

52:22.891 --> 52:25.060
And that's why he doesn't
wanna sleep with you.

52:25.226 --> 52:28.730
It's complicated
but that's what he said. Yes.

52:30.440 --> 52:33.777
I really wonder how he gets that.
Ask yourself.

52:34.736 --> 52:36.863
Because now it's my fault?

52:36.946 --> 52:39.074
I'm not assigning
blame, Franck.

52:39.199 --> 52:41.368
But you are always.

52:41.451 --> 52:42.786
You can't do it because
of this, because of that.

52:42.911 --> 52:46.247
There is always something but
it's never your fault, right?

52:46.581 --> 52:48.541
"It's a partnership, Franck."

52:48.625 --> 52:50.335
"He's got to
respect me, Franck."

52:51.211 --> 52:52.170
"We've gotta
make him feel safe."

52:52.253 --> 52:54.130
"We've gotta
show him our fear."

52:54.214 --> 52:57.550
"In an ideal world, Franck,
he'd kill us all."

52:58.259 --> 53:02.263
In an ideal world, Elizabeth,
you'd go hypnotize the guy.

53:02.430 --> 53:03.390
You'd bring me
back the painting

53:03.473 --> 53:06.935
and you'd stop
wasting my fucking time.

53:14.067 --> 53:15.068
Wait.

53:22.367 --> 53:23.493
<font color="#D900D9">(HEAVY BREATHING)</font>

53:27.664 --> 53:28.957
<font color="#D900D9">(MOANING CONTINUES)</font>

54:05.452 --> 54:06.453
<font color="#D900D9">(ALARM BEEPS)</font>

54:12.000 --> 54:13.293
<font color="#D900D9">(RINGING)</font>

54:15.628 --> 54:16.963
Jesus!

54:19.716 --> 54:23.720
Fucking hell.
<i>Simon, it's Nate. We need to talk.</i>

54:25.263 --> 54:26.598
Come up.
<font color="#D900D9">(BUZZING)</font>

54:33.396 --> 54:35.356
<font color="#D900D9">(<i>SANDMAN</i> BY
KIRSTY MCGEE PLAYING)</font>

54:41.529 --> 54:45.950
<i>Right before
you close your eyes</i>

54:46.034 --> 54:48.703
<i>Whispering your prayers</i>

54:50.705 --> 54:54.334
<i>When the sandman
blows your eyes</i>

54:54.417 --> 54:56.377
<i>I'll be there</i>

55:00.006 --> 55:02.258
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> I must remember
never to forget...

55:03.843 --> 55:05.428
...that you're a criminal.

55:19.984 --> 55:21.653
You got a boyfriend?

55:21.778 --> 55:23.446
Now you ask?
Mmm-hmm.

55:25.323 --> 55:26.324
No.

55:26.866 --> 55:28.451
I'm single.

55:29.410 --> 55:31.079
How is that possible?

55:32.372 --> 55:35.208
I was in a relationship...

55:36.543 --> 55:38.211
...he was violent...

55:39.087 --> 55:40.922
...so now I'm not.

55:42.924 --> 55:44.425
Got his address?

55:45.843 --> 55:47.679
That's very kind...

55:48.555 --> 55:50.181
...but 'no, thank you'.

55:50.682 --> 55:52.600
You should get even.

55:52.934 --> 55:54.602
Get a little angry.

55:55.853 --> 55:58.189
To be angry is to be a victim.

55:58.731 --> 56:00.316
I've moved on.

56:01.776 --> 56:04.112
That's the only real victory.

56:07.198 --> 56:08.199
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font>

56:09.659 --> 56:11.995
So why are you
doing this, then?

56:13.454 --> 56:15.456
Because it makes a change.

56:17.875 --> 56:21.129
If you had to deal
with morbid obesity and...

56:21.838 --> 56:23.506
...panic attacks...

56:25.800 --> 56:27.969
...you'd see the attraction.

56:34.142 --> 56:35.893
Can I tell you something?

56:42.150 --> 56:43.901
I'd rather not.

56:48.489 --> 56:52.619
<i>Gather roses while you may</i>

56:52.702 --> 56:55.747
<i>While the bloom is full</i>

56:57.206 --> 57:00.418
<i>For the blossom soon will fade</i>

57:00.501 --> 57:03.963
<i>And the bloom grows dull</i>

57:05.798 --> 57:10.094
<i>Right before you
close your eyes</i>

57:10.178 --> 57:12.972
<i>Whispering your prayers</i>

57:14.682 --> 57:18.186
<i>When the sandman
blows your eyes</i>

57:19.520 --> 57:21.356
<i>Who'll be there?</i>

57:38.956 --> 57:39.957
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> Hey.

57:42.001 --> 57:43.586
<font color="#D900D9">(FRANCK SIGHS)</font>

57:43.670 --> 57:45.046
Listen, I...

57:46.297 --> 57:47.548
...I...

57:49.801 --> 57:51.386
...can you...

57:52.553 --> 57:54.389
Can you see me again?

57:55.556 --> 57:58.393
It's not exactly what
I wanted to say, but...

58:00.186 --> 58:01.729
I mean, you know...

58:04.899 --> 58:07.694
Yeah. I think so.

58:10.238 --> 58:11.239
Good.

58:11.656 --> 58:12.657
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

58:14.992 --> 58:16.577
Be careful.

58:22.750 --> 58:26.003
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>And as the image
grows closer and clearer...</i>

58:26.087 --> 58:28.589
...you find you are watching
what he did to you.

58:28.756 --> 58:30.299
You are watching
the terrible things

58:30.383 --> 58:33.803
that he did.
But, with every blow...

58:33.928 --> 58:36.597
...that you watch
rain down upon you...

58:38.850 --> 58:42.103
...you become only more
determined than ever.

58:42.895 --> 58:45.523
<i>You know that it's possible...</i>

58:45.857 --> 58:48.609
<i>...to change your life
and move on.</i>

58:48.776 --> 58:51.362
That you will not
let this define you.

58:51.779 --> 58:55.575
You will not let yourself
be violated by the memory...

58:55.783 --> 58:58.453
...as you are
violated by the act.

59:10.798 --> 59:12.049
<font color="#D900D9">(ELEVATOR DINGS)</font>

59:23.478 --> 59:24.479
Simon?

59:26.230 --> 59:28.524
This all part of
your plan, yeah?

59:28.608 --> 59:29.689
What are you talking about?

59:29.734 --> 59:30.985
The two of you.

59:31.152 --> 59:34.155
Planning it together. Gonna get
it out of me and then dump me.

59:34.322 --> 59:35.782
Simon, will you
calm down, please.

59:35.865 --> 59:38.659
How long have you
been fucking Franck?

59:39.494 --> 59:40.828
Where did that come from?

59:40.912 --> 59:42.997
It's true, though, isn't it?

59:43.164 --> 59:44.165
You know it isn't.

59:44.248 --> 59:46.459
Why would Nate lie
about something like that?

59:46.584 --> 59:48.419
Because he wants Franck out.

59:48.503 --> 59:49.837
He wants the painting
for himself.

59:50.004 --> 59:52.006
I don't fucking believe you!

59:52.173 --> 59:56.844
Don't believe what? The existence
of greed in human beings? Grow up!

