01:19:23.760 --> 01:19:25.470
Okay, I get it.

01:19:25.553 --> 01:19:26.554
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHING)</font>

01:19:27.555 --> 01:19:29.808
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>She will do
anything for you.</i>

01:19:31.893 --> 01:19:33.728
<i>You fall in love...</i>

01:19:34.437 --> 01:19:36.606
<i>...with a kind of perfection.</i>

01:19:37.232 --> 01:19:39.150
<i>The kind you like.</i>

01:19:39.985 --> 01:19:41.945
You're an elephant?
No, I'm not an elephant.

01:19:42.070 --> 01:19:46.449
No, it's the Goya. It's 'The Witches In
The Air' that I was telling you about.

01:19:46.533 --> 01:19:47.534
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font>

01:19:51.037 --> 01:19:53.456
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>But then
you become possessive.</i>

01:19:55.208 --> 01:19:57.961
<i>Suspicious. Night and day...</i>

01:19:58.086 --> 01:20:02.090
...you fear that you will lose her.
It torments you.

01:20:04.592 --> 01:20:06.594
<i>And you become jealous.</i>

01:20:07.262 --> 01:20:09.389
Who are you texting?<font color="#808080">
ELIZABETH:</font> Sorry, work.

01:20:09.514 --> 01:20:11.975
<i>You start to believe that
you depend upon her.</i>

01:20:12.851 --> 01:20:15.353
<i>That without her you will die.</i>

01:20:16.396 --> 01:20:20.316
<i>You start to hate her
as much as you love her.</i>

01:20:22.027 --> 01:20:23.570
And then one evening...

01:20:23.695 --> 01:20:26.614
<i>...after you've accused her
of looking at another man...</i>

01:20:26.740 --> 01:20:28.408
You keep your mouth shut!

01:20:28.533 --> 01:20:31.953
Why don't you just sit down. Don't
they make a beautiful couple?

01:20:32.078 --> 01:20:35.123
You can just look at him now.
Just feast your fucking eyes!

01:20:35.248 --> 01:20:37.917
Elizabeth. No, I'm leaving.
I'm leaving.

01:20:45.717 --> 01:20:48.219
<i>She knows she has to get out.</i>

01:20:48.428 --> 01:20:49.429
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font>

01:20:49.512 --> 01:20:53.183
She has to break it off
but you won't let her go.

01:20:53.266 --> 01:20:54.809
You persist.

01:20:55.727 --> 01:21:00.982
<i>You apologize. You write long letters
vowing never to do it again.</i>

01:21:01.441 --> 01:21:03.401
<i>You weep, you call.</i>

01:21:03.526 --> 01:21:05.111
She is frightened.

01:21:05.236 --> 01:21:07.280
I need to talk to
you for 2 minutes.

01:21:07.489 --> 01:21:09.699
<i>Really frightened now.
Please let me come in.</i>

01:21:10.241 --> 01:21:12.660
<i>And she knows
if this goes on...</i>

01:21:13.870 --> 01:21:16.164
...there can be
only one outcome.

01:21:16.915 --> 01:21:18.750
Hi. How are you doing?

01:21:19.501 --> 01:21:23.713
<font color="#808080">SIMON:</font> I just need you to let me
apologize and see that you accept that.

01:21:23.838 --> 01:21:25.215
I need to see that in your eyes

01:21:25.298 --> 01:21:28.510
and then I'll leave
you alone. I promise.

01:21:28.968 --> 01:21:30.553
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>In the end...</i>

01:21:32.222 --> 01:21:35.391
<i>...she knows that you will kill her.</i>
<font color="#D900D9">(GROANING)</font>

01:21:36.101 --> 01:21:39.229
Please, stop!
Simon, you're hurting me.

01:21:39.354 --> 01:21:41.606
It's okay.
No, it's not okay.

01:21:42.315 --> 01:21:44.651
<i>The police are not interested.</i>

01:21:45.193 --> 01:21:49.072
<i>Lawyers advise her to change her
name, to leave the country...</i>

01:21:49.197 --> 01:21:51.199
<i>...but she will not do this.</i>

01:21:53.701 --> 01:21:56.538
<i>She will not be
a victim twice over.</i>

01:21:59.249 --> 01:22:01.668
<i>Instead, she will take control.</i>

01:22:02.585 --> 01:22:04.796
So she perverts the therapy...

01:22:05.338 --> 01:22:07.757
<i>you've insisted on continuing.</i>

01:22:08.508 --> 01:22:09.509
Simon...

01:22:11.594 --> 01:22:14.222
...it's not the gambling
that you want to forget.

01:22:14.556 --> 01:22:16.224
It's me.

01:22:18.309 --> 01:22:20.436
You want to forget me.

01:22:21.437 --> 01:22:23.773
You made me forget?

01:22:25.275 --> 01:22:27.485
She makes you want to forget.

01:22:29.487 --> 01:22:31.322
You're forgetting me.

01:22:33.449 --> 01:22:35.368
You're forgetting us.

01:22:35.493 --> 01:22:39.289
And you feel so much more relaxed.
So much more free.

01:22:39.414 --> 01:22:40.415
Leave.
<font color="#D900D9">(SNAPS FINGERS)</font>

01:22:43.376 --> 01:22:46.171
<i>And gradually...
day by day...</i>

01:22:47.255 --> 01:22:50.175
...week by week you do.

01:22:51.217 --> 01:22:52.927
You call less often.

01:22:54.012 --> 01:22:56.598
The passions subside.

01:22:57.473 --> 01:22:59.642
<i>You're late for therapy.</i>

01:23:00.643 --> 01:23:03.980
<i>Then one day
you don't come at all.</i>

01:23:04.772 --> 01:23:08.985
<i>At last you have suppressed
the memory of me.</i>

01:23:14.616 --> 01:23:16.201
But you knew.

01:23:19.954 --> 01:23:22.457
<i>You knew I'd come back...</i>

01:23:22.790 --> 01:23:24.292
<i>...one day.</i>

01:23:26.336 --> 01:23:28.880
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>Your memory
is not destroyed.</i>

01:23:29.005 --> 01:23:31.257
<i>It is locked in a cage.</i>

01:23:32.425 --> 01:23:34.344
<i>And with enough...</i>

01:23:34.469 --> 01:23:35.803
<i>...force...</i>

01:23:36.888 --> 01:23:38.806
<i>...enough violence...</i>

01:23:39.307 --> 01:23:41.643
<i>...the lock can be broken.</i>

01:23:48.608 --> 01:23:50.944
It comes back, the memory.

01:23:51.694 --> 01:23:53.321
Not completely.

01:23:53.738 --> 01:23:57.575
<i>Not entirely,
but enough to drive you...</i>

01:23:57.700 --> 01:24:00.411
...to make you feel
you have been cheated.

01:24:01.955 --> 01:24:04.249
Enough to make you angry.

01:24:04.374 --> 01:24:05.375
Franck!

01:24:05.458 --> 01:24:06.459
<font color="#D900D9">(MOBILE BUZZING)</font>

01:24:09.045 --> 01:24:10.046
<font color="#D900D9">(TIRES SCREECHING)</font>

01:24:15.218 --> 01:24:17.095
What did she look like?

01:24:19.681 --> 01:24:20.682
You.

01:24:20.765 --> 01:24:21.975
<font color="#D900D9">(SIMON PANTING)</font>

01:24:22.183 --> 01:24:23.768
God, are you all right?

01:24:24.269 --> 01:24:25.311
Elizabeth.

01:24:25.687 --> 01:24:27.480
No, I'm not Elizabeth.

01:24:27.605 --> 01:24:29.482
Shall I call for an ambulance?

01:24:29.607 --> 01:24:31.192
I remember.

01:24:32.277 --> 01:24:33.903
I remember everything.

01:24:33.987 --> 01:24:35.697
Why don't I take
you to hospital?

01:24:37.657 --> 01:24:39.867
As the memory comes back...

01:24:39.993 --> 01:24:40.994
Okay?

01:24:41.411 --> 01:24:44.330
Shall I help you with your seat belt?
Why did you lie to me?

01:24:44.747 --> 01:24:47.166
What?
You made me forget.

01:24:49.752 --> 01:24:51.504
Okay, maybe I should just
call for that ambulance.

01:24:51.587 --> 01:24:52.588
Elizabeth!

01:24:52.839 --> 01:24:55.591
Will you let go of me, please?
I don't want you to go.

01:24:56.342 --> 01:24:57.969
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font>
I don't want you to go.

01:24:58.386 --> 01:24:59.679
<font color="#D900D9">(WEEPING)</font> And then...

01:24:59.804 --> 01:25:02.557
Look, I'm sorry, whoever
Elizabeth is, she isn't me.

01:25:02.640 --> 01:25:03.641
<font color="#D900D9">(CHOKING)</font>

01:25:08.271 --> 01:25:09.272
<font color="#D900D9">(WEEPING)</font>

01:25:11.858 --> 01:25:13.026
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font>

01:25:26.372 --> 01:25:27.373
<font color="#D900D9">(CAR ALARM CHIRPING)</font>

01:25:47.143 --> 01:25:50.480
<font color="#808080">ELIZABETH:</font> <i>A few months
later you came back.</i>

01:25:52.607 --> 01:25:54.233
Mr. Maxwell?

01:25:56.361 --> 01:25:57.945
Mr. Maxwell?

01:25:59.155 --> 01:26:00.406
That's...

01:26:01.532 --> 01:26:03.034
...that's me.

01:26:06.788 --> 01:26:07.789
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHING)</font>

01:26:08.498 --> 01:26:10.291
Is something the matter?

01:26:13.336 --> 01:26:15.004
Of course not.

01:26:15.296 --> 01:26:17.965
I'm Elizabeth... Lamb.

01:26:18.591 --> 01:26:20.843
<i>You've come to
find your car keys.</i>

01:26:20.927 --> 01:26:22.637
<i>Well, they're just
right in here.</i>

01:26:22.762 --> 01:26:23.763
Stop.

01:26:27.809 --> 01:26:29.977
Can you give her
the keys, Franck?

01:26:43.574 --> 01:26:45.201
It's in the back.

01:26:56.462 --> 01:26:57.797
<font color="#D900D9">(WATER DRIPPING)</font>

01:27:14.730 --> 01:27:16.107
<font color="#D900D9">(FLIES BUZZING)</font>

01:27:20.403 --> 01:27:21.863
<font color="#D900D9">(MOANS IN DISGUST)</font>
<font color="#D900D9">(KEYS CLATTER)</font>

01:27:24.532 --> 01:27:26.159
Is it there, Elizabeth?

01:27:28.661 --> 01:27:29.704
<font color="#D900D9">(FLIES CONTINUE BUZZING)</font>

01:27:29.787 --> 01:27:31.914
Elizabeth, is it there?!

01:27:31.998 --> 01:27:32.999
<font color="#D900D9">(GAGS)</font>

01:27:49.891 --> 01:27:51.559
<font color="#D900D9">(SOBBING)</font> I'm sorry.

01:28:19.378 --> 01:28:21.047
I don't want it.

01:28:23.090 --> 01:28:25.593
I don't know that
lever really did.

01:28:32.058 --> 01:28:34.143
Maybe you can tell me sometime.

01:28:46.447 --> 01:28:47.448
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> No!

01:28:58.209 --> 01:28:59.335
No.

01:28:59.418 --> 01:29:01.837
No, no, no...

01:29:01.921 --> 01:29:03.172
<font color="#D900D9">(BOTH GRUNTING)</font>

01:29:05.716 --> 01:29:08.594
Simon, you don't
have to do this.

01:29:09.262 --> 01:29:13.391
I want... to forget
that you did all this.

01:29:15.560 --> 01:29:16.561
<font color="#D900D9">(CRIES OUT)</font>

01:29:20.606 --> 01:29:21.691
<font color="#D900D9">(YELLING)</font>

01:29:25.069 --> 01:29:26.070
No.

01:29:29.115 --> 01:29:30.116
<font color="#D900D9">(GUNSHOT)</font>

01:29:43.087 --> 01:29:44.088
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> Please!

01:29:45.006 --> 01:29:46.007
<font color="#D900D9">(HORN BLARING)</font>

01:29:55.975 --> 01:29:56.976
<font color="#D900D9">(CAR ALARM BLARING)</font>

01:30:08.696 --> 01:30:10.072
<font color="#D900D9">(ENGINE STARTING)</font>

01:30:14.493 --> 01:30:15.494
<font color="#D900D9">(GUN CLICKING)</font>

01:30:33.888 --> 01:30:35.014
<font color="#D900D9">(ENGINE REVVING)</font>

01:31:09.048 --> 01:31:10.549
Bring it to me.

01:31:15.221 --> 01:31:16.222
<font color="#D900D9">(YELLING)</font>

01:31:36.992 --> 01:31:38.411
<font color="#808080">FRANCK:</font> Stop, please!

01:31:42.707 --> 01:31:43.708
<font color="#D900D9">(SCREAMS)</font>

01:31:43.791 --> 01:31:44.792
<font color="#D900D9">(PANTING)</font>

01:31:56.470 --> 01:31:58.264
<font color="#D900D9">(<i>HERE IT COMES</i>
BY EMELI SANDÃ PLAYING)</font>

01:32:16.824 --> 01:32:18.242
Are you okay?

01:32:19.118 --> 01:32:20.119
No!

01:32:29.128 --> 01:32:30.171
Hey!

01:32:36.385 --> 01:32:38.387
Shall I tell you something?

01:32:44.351 --> 01:32:46.020
I'd rather not.

01:32:47.396 --> 01:32:48.856
<font color="#D900D9">(DOORBELL RINGS)</font>

01:32:52.818 --> 01:32:54.820
There's a parcel for Le Pere.

01:32:56.113 --> 01:32:57.448
Thank you.

01:33:13.130 --> 01:33:14.799
<i>Hello, Franck.</i>

01:33:16.008 --> 01:33:17.468
<i>It looks good...</i>

01:33:18.260 --> 01:33:19.929
<i>...don't you think?</i>

01:33:20.179 --> 01:33:21.972
<i>Hanging on the wall.</i>

01:33:23.516 --> 01:33:26.852
<i>I thought it might make me
think too much of him, but...</i>

01:33:28.354 --> 01:33:30.356
<i>...instead I think of you.</i>

01:33:31.023 --> 01:33:34.360
<i>You want me to send
it back, don't you?</i>

01:33:35.361 --> 01:33:37.696
<i>Or sell it...</i>

01:33:37.863 --> 01:33:40.449
<i>...and divide the money.</i>

01:33:41.700 --> 01:33:42.701
<i>But...</i>

01:33:44.495 --> 01:33:46.664
<i>...you know I can't do that.</i>

01:33:48.874 --> 01:33:51.335
<i>Not when it means
so much to me.</i>

01:33:52.545 --> 01:33:55.047
<i>Not when I've worked
so hard for it.</i>

01:33:55.548 --> 01:33:58.467
<i>Simon, you're forgetting me.</i>

01:34:00.302 --> 01:34:02.388
You're forgetting us.

01:34:02.513 --> 01:34:05.224
Even when you have forgotten
the one you love...

01:34:05.891 --> 01:34:07.643
<i>...you will gamble...</i>

01:34:08.060 --> 01:34:10.521
<i>...lie, cheat...</i>

01:34:11.230 --> 01:34:12.731
...and steal.

01:34:13.399 --> 01:34:14.400
<font color="#808080">FRANCIS:</font> Sold!

01:34:14.567 --> 01:34:16.735
Steal for her a painting.

01:34:18.153 --> 01:34:19.738
<i>Simon, a painting...</i>

01:34:20.322 --> 01:34:22.241
<i>...for the woman you hurt.</i>

01:34:22.908 --> 01:34:25.327
For the woman you left behind.

01:34:28.038 --> 01:34:29.039
<font color="#D900D9">(MOBILE VIBRATING)</font>

01:34:36.839 --> 01:34:37.840
<font color="#D900D9">(TIRES SCREECHING)</font>

01:34:37.923 --> 01:34:38.924
<font color="#D900D9">(SNAPS)</font>

01:34:40.843 --> 01:34:44.597
<i>Now perhaps,
some day, you'll find me.</i>

01:34:45.681 --> 01:34:47.308
<i>I hope that you do.</i>

01:34:48.350 --> 01:34:51.270
<i>But, if it's all too much...</i>

01:34:51.854 --> 01:34:54.356
<i>...if you wish
that we'd never met...</i>

01:34:56.442 --> 01:34:58.611
<i>...that it had
never happened...</i>

01:34:59.236 --> 01:35:01.572
<i>...I can make it
go away, Franck.</i>

01:35:01.697 --> 01:35:04.158
<i>All you have to do
is touch the screen.</i>

01:35:04.450 --> 01:35:06.201
<i>Press right here...</i>

01:35:08.704 --> 01:35:11.332
<i>...and follow my voice.</i>

01:35:11.624 --> 01:35:13.792
<i>The choice is yours.</i>

01:35:13.918 --> 01:35:17.129
<i>Do you want to
remember... or...</i>

01:35:17.379 --> 01:35:20.883
<i>...do you want to forget?</i>

01:35:26.263 --> 01:35:27.264
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

01:35:29.516 --> 01:35:30.517
<font color="#D900D9">(CLICKS TONGUE)</font>

